# Project standards

## Stack

- **Next.js 16**, React 19, TypeScript. App Router only.

## Formatting (Prettier)

- No semicolons; single quotes; trailing commas everywhere; 80 print width; 2-space indent.
- Import order: `react` → `next` → third-party → `@/components` → `@/hooks` → `@/lib` → `@/utils` → relative.

## Paths

- Use `@/` for app root: `@/components`, `@/hooks`, `@/lib`, `@/utils`.

## Quality

- Run `npm run lint` before committing. Pre-commit runs ESLint and `prettier --check .`.
